        "shortName": "G95K",
        "description": "The G95K handguard is a lightweight, free-floating handguard designed for the G95K rifle platform. It features a modular design with multiple attachment points for accessories such as lights, lasers, and grips. The handguard is constructed from high-quality aluminum alloy, providing durability and strength while maintaining a lightweight profile. Its ergonomic design ensures a comfortable grip and improved handling during shooting. This variant comes in a Flat Dark Earth (FDE) finish, offering enhanced camouflage in desert and arid environments."
      }
